### STEP 5 — After applying patch, the mermaid-render skill can write:
```bash
# Write upload request to IPC messages dir
echo '{
  "type": "file_upload",
  "chatJid": "slack:C0AMR0DRDFG",
  "filePath": "/tmp/my-diagram.png",
  "caption": "🗺️ Wardley Map: Golden Dome Technology Landscape"
}' > /workspace/ipc/messages/upload-$(date +%s%N).json
```
The host picks this up within ~1 second and uploads as a native Slack file. No external services. 🥐
